        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>A cone of icy shards bursts from your spread hands and coats the target in a layer of frost. You deal 2d4 cold damage to creatures in the area; they must each attempt a Reflex save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><span><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and takes a -5-foot status penalty to its Speeds for 2 rounds.</span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and takes a -10-foot status penalty to its Speeds for 2 rounds.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d4.</p>"
